div.div:
The Wanjie Continent is filled with prodigies, acclaimed as deities, princes, and taoists, representing the future of each sect. The untalented and ordinary Qin Shu was supposed to one of these prodigies due to his father, one of the strongest men on the continent. But instead he was looked down and jeered upon by everyone in his sect. Until one day, his Wanjie Checkin System finally reached 100%, and all of a sudden he reached peak power by unlocking the skill of Perpetual Dantian!
(Source: Tencent, translated)

To avenge his older brother, an orphan named Jongli Chu killed Hwang Jung, a Heaven-slaying sect disciple. Following the death of Hwang-Jung, he joined the Imitating Blade killer of Soul-killing Chambers to avoid the pursuit of the Heaven-slaying Sect. However, a huge mess called ten chastisements was waiting for him.
To escape the shadow of chastisement, he has no choice but to become a Legendary Death God! Can Jongli Chu become a Death God and find freedom in the stifling rules created by the Orthodox Sects?
(Source: Naver, translated)
